      "description": "Hi everyone! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly flawless shape\u2014it honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous with maintenance, and it drives like an absolute dream. You won't find a single blemish on it, inside or out. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it for yourself!",
