      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of the S54 platform, featuring a high-revving 3.2L inline-six with a fully overhauled double-VANOS system and documented rod bearing replacement. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with a reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis rigidity under lateral load. Every mechanical component, from the individual throttle bodies to the variable M-differential, functions at factory-spec tolerances. With an immaculate undercarriage and a flawless interior, this is a turnkey, collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
